# `ATTRIBUTION.md`

```markdown
# Attribution & ToS notes (initial providers)

Display a visible source label on each job card (e.g., “Source: Remotive”) linking to the job’s original URL when possible. Some providers **require** attribution and/or usage constraints.

> This page is a quick reminder; always check each provider’s live terms before shipping.

---

## Remotive — **Required**
- **Do not** submit Remotive jobs to third-party sites (e.g., Jooble, Talent.com/Neuvoo, Google Jobs, LinkedIn Jobs).
- **Must** link back to the Remotive job URL **and** mention Remotive as a source; they can terminate API access for non-compliance. :contentReference[oaicite:6]{index=6}

**UI rule:** Show “Source: Remotive” linking to the Remotive listing.

---

## Arbeitnow — **Link back requested**
- Terms state: *“You also agree to providing a link back to Arbeitnow.com on your platform.”* :contentReference[oaicite:7]{index=7}

**UI rule:** Show “Source: Arbeitnow” linking to the Arbeitnow listing or homepage.

---

## Jobicy — **Public feeds; attribution recommended**
- Jobicy advertises public API/RSS/XML feeds for remote jobs. No explicit attribution line on the feed page, but linking back is good practice. :contentReference[oaicite:8]{index=8}

**UI rule:** Show “Source: Jobicy” linking to the Jobicy listing when available.

---

## USAJOBS — **Headers required; respect rate limits**
- Use required headers: `Host: data.usajobs.gov`, `User-Agent: <your email>`, `Authorization-Key: <your key>`. Base URL: `https://data.usajobs.gov/api/search`. :contentReference[oaicite:9]{index=9}
- USAJOBS provides guides on **Rate Limiting** and **Terms of Use**; follow them. :contentReference[oaicite:10]{index=10}

**UI rule:** Show “Source: USAJOBS (OPM)” linking to the announcement if provided.

---

## Jooble — **Key required; follow Help Center docs**
- Obtain a free key and call `POST /api/{api_key}` as documented. :contentReference[oaicite:11]{index=11}

**UI rule:** Show “Source: Jooble” linking to the listing/company page when provided.

---

## Adzuna — **Required**
- ToS requires labeling each displayed advert with **“Jobs by Adzuna”**, with the text/logo **hyperlinked** to the relevant Adzuna domain; additional branding rules apply. :contentReference[oaicite:12]{index=12}
- Register for `app_id` and `app_key`; interactive docs list endpoints like `/jobs/{country}/search/{page}`. :contentReference[oaicite:13]{index=13}

**UI rule:** Include the “Jobs by Adzuna” label/logo per ToS, linking to the local Adzuna site.

---

## General etiquette
- Refresh politely (respect your local RPM throttles).
- Keep original links intact to drive traffic back to sources.
- If a provider updates terms, update `ATTRIBUTION.md` and `config/providers.yaml` before your next deploy.
